abstract: Johan Olsson wins men's 15-kilometer freestyle race for his second cross-country skiing world title.
lead_paragraph: The cross-country skier Johan Olsson of Sweden took advantage of an early start number to win the men’s 15-kilometer freestyle race for his second world title.
snippet: The cross-country skier Johan Olsson of Sweden took advantage of an early start number to win the men’s 15-kilometer freestyle race for his second world title.
